+// This is "Layer 2" of the design's test plan: unit tests for the generic
+// scope-filtering bypass branch in withAuthorization, isolated from the
+// storage layer entirely (no *genericregistry.Store, no resolvers -- just
+// the HTTP-level gate that decides whether a denied request is handed to
